{"tid":1486851,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"内地驚現 Supreme Tea 台茶店？明知假都照打卡","createTime":"2019-08-19T04:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T06:14:01.000Z","uid":44569,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f5a9e9011a9598649d76cc6986d443ab80cf80bf","tid":1486851,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uayog0Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuayog0Q.jpg&h=165e9f33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSupreme 盜版風波持續。正當中國商標局正式撤銷盜版 Supreme Italia 的商標權，中國内地又出現了一間名為「Supreme Tea」的台茶店。沒想到現在連盜版的 Supreme 台式飲品都有？<br />\n<br />\n今年 7 月一間打著 Supreme 旗號的台茶店在深圳開幕，引來外媒實地「潛入」看看情況。從照片可見，「Supreme Tea」店外掛著超大個 Supreme Logo，而店員的衣服、紙杯、牆壁、裝飾品上全部均印有「Supreme」Logo，驟眼一看會覺得超像紐約的 Supreme 專門店。跟其他台茶店一樣，「Supreme Tea」提供果茶、奶昔、咖啡等，還有一款「回轉冰」，平均 ￥20 到 ￥30（約 HK $24 到 $36），價格算合理。配上紅底白字 Supreme 的紙杯，的確能滿足打卡的虛榮心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hzaYQkY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhzaYQkY.jpg&h=181ce641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好笑的是，店内在裝飾上下了不少苦功。除了 Supreme，還在牆壁上加了各個包括 Levi's、adidas、Air Jordan 等潮牌商標上去，更有侵侵、中指貓等插畫，可以説是「潮流大雜燴」，什麽都有。雖然店鋪依然有不少人光顧前去打卡，但「Supreme Tea」在 社交平台上則引來大量批評。有内地網民甚至「翻牆」到 Instagram，留言大罵：「丟臉」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kQOPczp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkQOPczp.jpg&h=8b037ce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2428832/内地驚現%20Supreme%20Tea%20台茶店？明知假都照打卡\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2428832%2F%E5%86%85%E5%9C%B0%E9%A9%9A%E7%8F%BE%2520Supreme%2520Tea%2520%E5%8F%B0%E8%8C%B6%E5%BA%97%EF%BC%9F%E6%98%8E%E7%9F%A5%E5%81%87%E9%83%BD%E7%85%A7%E6%89%93%E5%8D%A1&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=0db5587a\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2428832/内地驚現%20Supreme%20Tea%20台茶店？明知假都照打卡</a></span>"},{"pid":"f332918b436003648b82208d71882acd566c8ffe","tid":1486851,"uid":122134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:17:49.000Z","msg":"應該叫superme<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae20e0e1842039515771bb94c5d18edf21f5f7ec","tid":1486851,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babba1ab171f21bb252294822297e8187b203667","tid":1486851,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae20e0e1842039515771bb94c5d18edf21f5f7ec","tid":1486851,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a86bbac4dd33caf73872c79ecfee8e90b0ea37e","tid":1486851,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:11:10.000Z","msg":"支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f84f2c602aad1567f6585124c78bba98a0e6391","tid":1486851,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ebbb40394c03c30260f33fbece1d4555d13d5c","tid":1486851,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}